{"tid":874480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[咩玩法?]珠海交通警：內地普通牌汽車不能進港珠澳大橋珠海連接線","createTime":"2018-10-24T08:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T09:28:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"234448914686d880b5a2adfa3ab371c4741d67ce","tid":874480,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"今天是一個喜大普奔的日子，港珠澳大橋正式開通小編有一個緊急通知要告訴大家： <br />\n<br />\n明天起，這些車不能進入珠澳口岸人工島，港珠澳大橋珠海連接線，珠澳 ！ 口岸人工島原施工便橋具體通告如下：<br />\n<br />\n為維護港珠澳大橋珠澳口岸人工島及珠海連接線良好交通秩序， <strong>現決定從2018年10月24日0時起，禁止內地普通號牌機動車進入珠澳口岸人工島，港珠澳大橋珠海連接線（南灣互通至珠澳口岸人工島），珠澳口岸人工島原施工便橋（情侶南路路口至珠澳口岸人工島）</strong>。具備通行港珠澳大橋資質的機動車，公共汽車和已備案的工作車輛除外。<br />\n<br />\n交警部門將在情侶南路路口，南灣互通等進入珠澳口岸人工島的入口進行交通管制，嚴格執法， 對於違反上述規定的機動車依法進行處罰。希望廣大市民遊客不要盲目開車前往珠澳口岸人工島！<br />\n<br />\n來源：珠海交警<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=en&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2018-10-23%2Fdoc-ihmuuiyw5821669.shtml&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftranslate.google.com.hk%2Ftranslate%3Fsl%3Den%26tl%3Dzh-TW%26js%3Dy%26prev%3D_t%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ie%3DUTF-8%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.sina.com.cn%252Fo%252F2018-10-23%252Fdoc-ihmuuiyw5821669.shtml%26edit-text%3D%26act%3Durl&d=pHDFri3JC9cxyroEx5P5vNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ac924291\" target=\"_blank\">https://translate.google.com.hk/translate?sl=en&amp;tl=zh-TW&amp;js=y&amp;prev=_t&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2018-10-23%2Fdoc-ihmuuiyw5821669.shtml&amp;edit-text=&amp;act=url</a>[/url]"},{"pid":"0a5e92a1006f40b498ac9445f235784d24a27f32","tid":874480,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"海關無片收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49356369a64b889ecb34cf4c317c778705ef3ca","tid":874480,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl